{"tid":1488479,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【買月餅認住呢間】 香港餅舖推出「反送中」月餅","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:47:02.000Z","uid":193565,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f91b2aea5f9f404efa412af6d4f8ba9991cc92","tid":1488479,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"〔編譯劉宜庭／綜合報導〕美聯社19日報導，香港華爾登餅店為了表達支持「反送中」抗爭，將香港人、不撤不散、一齊撐等字樣印在月餅上，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n餅舖經營者孫芷玲（Naomi Suen）告訴美聯社，「反送中月餅」的初衷是替政治動盪的香港社會帶來正面力量，「我希望能用這些餅幫香港人加油打氣」。<br />\n<br />\n餅舖顧客林姍蒂（Sandy Lam，譯音）告訴美聯社，這款月餅可以為社會運動發聲，反映出抗爭者的「真實情況」。餅面上印有的字句包括「香港人」、「不撤不散」、「一齊撐」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n報導特別指出，根據中國民間故事，中秋節月餅的由來正是在元朝末年，人民不堪暴政，遂透過互贈夾紙條的餅傳遞消息，揭竿起義；故事背景與當前香港民間社會氛圍也有幾分雷同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2889580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2889580&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAJBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=299cb461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2889580&h=9b851380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2889580</a>"},{"pid":"f7d00c4bbe8b2c844c737c938ca3382b5fba2187","tid":1488479,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思 麻煩大家幫手投票定個死線<br />\n大家既訴求唔可以不了了之</span></span><br />\n死線投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"397a0daf9d6cab00a2877b3903196dd720f4e85b","tid":1488479,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3540358c1f5cc2137958df7344e6a23a683ad45","tid":1488479,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"[8.19] 係咪覺得今日好多帶風向POST？幫你一